Package: clipd
Version: VERSION
Architecture: ARCH
Maintainer: kantha2004
Description: Clipboard history manager for Wayland/X11
 A keyboard-driven clipboard history daemon with a system-tray picker.
 Supports Wayland (wl-copy, ydotool) and X11 (xdotool).
Depends: libc6, libgl1, libx11-6, libbsd0, libxcb1
Recommends: wl-clipboard, ydotool | xdotool
